---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import LegalPage from "../../components/LegalPage.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - About Berlin Hotels"
  description="GDPR-compliant privacy policy for About Berlin Hotels."
  locale="en"
  alternatePath="/datenschutz/"
  noindex
>
  <LegalPage title="Privacy Policy" locale="en">
    <p>
      We take the protection of your personal data seriously. This privacy policy informs you about how your personal data
      is processed when you use this website (GDPR-compliant).
    </p>

    <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>[Name / company]</strong><br />
      [Address]<br />
      Email: <a href="mailto:info@about-berlin-hotels.de">info@about-berlin-hotels.de</a>
    </p>

    <h2>2. Server log files</h2>
    <p>
      When you access our website, our hosting provider automatically records information in server log files (IP address,
      date and time, browser type, etc.). Legal basis is Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR (legitimate interest in a technically functional
      website).
    </p>

    <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We use cookies on this website. Technically necessary cookies are set on the basis of Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR. Optional
      cookies (e.g. statistics, marketing) are only set after your explicit consent (Art. 6 (1) (a) GDPR) - see the cookie banner.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Google Tag Manager &amp; Google Analytics 4</h2>
    <p>
      If you consent, we use Google Tag Manager and Google Analytics 4 (Google Ireland Ltd., Dublin 4, Ireland). Data is
      processed in anonymised form (IP masking active). Legal basis: Art. 6 (1) (a) GDPR. Withdraw consent at any time via
      the cookie banner.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Stay22 hotel maps (embedded)</h2>
    <p>
      On individual pages we embed interactive maps by <strong>Stay22 Inc.</strong> (Canada) which display hotel offers from
      third parties such as Booking.com. Loading the map transmits your IP address to Stay22. Provider privacy policy:
      <a href="https://www.stay22.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">stay22.com/privacy</a>.
      Legal basis: Art. 6 (1) (a) GDPR (consent) or Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR (legitimate interest).
    </p>

    <h2>6. Google Fonts</h2>
    <p>
      We load the „Inter" font via Google Fonts. Loading transmits your IP to Google. Legal basis: Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR
      (optimisation of font rendering).
    </p>

    <h2>7. Affiliate programs</h2>
    <p>
      We participate in the Booking.com affiliate program (via Stay22) and may participate in further partner programs.
      Clicking an affiliate link redirects you to the provider's website. We may receive a commission.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Your rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Access to your stored data (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Rectification of incorrect data (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Erasure of your data (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Objection to processing (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Complaint to the competent supervisory authority (Art. 77 GDPR)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>9. Contact for data protection inquiries</h2>
    <p>
      For data protection questions, please contact us at:
      <a href="mailto:info@about-berlin-hotels.de">info@about-berlin-hotels.de</a>
    </p>
  </LegalPage>
</BaseLayout>
